```python
#6 Calculate Simple Interest
Principal_amount=int(input("Enter Principal Amount:"))
Rate_of_Interest=float(input("Enter Annual Interest Rate:"))
Time_in_Years=int(input("Enter Time(in years):"))

#Initiate Simple Interest Formula
Simple_Interest= (Principal_amount*Rate_of_Interest*Time_in_Years)/100

#print Simple Interest
print("Simple Interest:",Simple_Interest)
```

OUTPUT :Enter Principal Amount: 39800
        Enter Annual Interest Rate: 2.4
        Enter Time(in years): 4
        
        Simple Interest: 3820.8
